\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Background Layer:
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The interior storefronts, escalators, or mall hallways. This stays entirely static.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	2.	}
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Character Layer (The Guard):
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The security guard sprite or silhouette. Python will move his X-coordinate left and right to simulate his patrol.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	3.	}
