\fs28\fsmilli14118 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 random
\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  library to introduce natural, unpredictable behaviors.\
Instead of a constant back-and-forth loop, your code can use a simple 
