\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 3. Coding the Evolving Mall Atmosphere\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 The magic of your 6-hour video comes from the environment evolving around the guard. Since you want to keep costs at absolute zero, you can use Python to manipulate the 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Background Layer
