\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 4. Preventing "Visual Exhaustion"\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 A single hallway might get visually tiring after 3 hours. Because your camera is perpendicular to the walls, you can easily code a 
